[{"client_msg_id":"bbeae2cb-195f-464a-8ce5-b89d00698853","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"おー全部知らなかった… それぞれ Web UI / GUI / TUI ついてるのか\n調べてみます","ts":"1584774423.002700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"UR004"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"f272d35c-dc06-472a-a223-4f40a179c323","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"自宅サーバを docker で管理したくて、ノードは2台でこのコンテナはこっち（ノードA）、このコンテンツはこっち（ノードB）みたいに設定や CLI から指定したいです。\nこういうのやるには k8s とかがいいんでしょうか","ts":"1584722183.048300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"rAcTI"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"358a62e1-4ce4-480b-a313-ace1bc2977d0","type":"message","user":"UNJ2DANJC","text":"その用途だとまさにk8sですね \nnodeSelectorとかAffinityで特定のノードにpodを寄せられますね。\nただステートフルな要素（ストレージとか）が絡んでくると色々めんどくさいとは思います。","ts":"1584722744.052200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"pRG"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"850e6876-5873-4e49-83ff-de67eb2af5f9","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"なるほど\nストレージは RAID 付きの HDD ケース（裸族の～みたいなやつとか）につないでファイルサーバのデータもコンテナのデータもなんもかんもそこにぶっこもうと思ってます（自宅サーバで mdadm とか LVM とかもう疲れちゃった…）","ts":"1584723016.054300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"rya"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"727a6616-1364-48f2-be82-1f7357584c64","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"2台体制で冗長化してサービスごとに分けようかと思ってます… いやユーザ数=1なんだから負荷考えなくてよくて夜中にまとめてバックアップとかでもいいんだよな…うーん","ts":"1584723116.056400","edited":{"user":"U0M7GCBPD","ts":"1584723139.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"X0n"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"62a63ae4-1bbf-40f4-bbf9-91d694e565b6","type":"message","user":"UNJ2DANJC","text":"個人的にはよっぽどのこと（GPU付きノードに載せないといけないとか）がない限り特定のノードに寄せずにk8sのスケジューラに全部おまかせでいいんじゃないかと思ってます。","ts":"1584723221.057800","edited":{"user":"UNJ2DANJC","ts":"1584723241.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"OLI"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"38d75120-d9b1-4fe9-b1f4-dd082336c95f","type":"message","user":"UNJ2DANJC","text":"（自宅サーバにk8sは明らかにオーバースペックなので学習/管理コストのほうが上回るとは思います...）","ts":"1584723423.059300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"4k6oS"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"d31d1048-346d-47e9-9078-d0c23805fa12","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"（正直学習も兼ねてます…）","ts":"1584723460.059700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"4aBlD"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"a7a271ef-1c9b-4a7a-9f1e-f475681114d8","type":"message","user":"UNJ2DANJC","text":"いきなり自前クラスタは構築から難易度高いのでマネージドとかkind, minikubeで慣れてからが良いと思います。マネージドも面倒みるの結構大変...","ts":"1584723614.062100","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"eyes","count":1,"users":["U0M7GCBPD"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"LaR03"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"8cc657b1-19cd-4485-af35-cd5c81538829","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"おお、見てみます。正直学習も兼ねてるとはいえ自宅サーバ復活の目的の方が大きいので…","ts":"1584723697.062800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"o0lMk"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"e0a389ac-713e-4dbd-8d3a-759cc243a60e","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"スケジューラって無効にして手動でノード指定もできたりします？","ts":"1584723723.063200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"M0/AE"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"ebcd3efd-abad-4a40-87b0-c19b324d1838","type":"message","user":"UNJ2DANJC","text":"無効はできるのか... ちょっとわかりません... このラベルのついたnodeに置いてくれってスケジューラにお願いする感じです","ts":"1584723850.064500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"gFN"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"43f0c1b8-d9b7-4cd4-9f5b-7d553da376fe","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"ふむふむ\n2台に active, standby 割り当てて全部 active に置けばよさそう？","ts":"1584723952.065600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"tT7q"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"be44f6b2-4828-4ecc-a4ac-184d9ddcb86a","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"もうなんかディストリビューションというかベアメタルというか、インストールしさえすればシュッと k8s 環境が手に入るならそれでもいい（学習も兼ねている、とは…）","ts":"1584724050.067800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"IJmI"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"12357c76-cb8e-40fe-8891-9ad9a908eea8","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"いや流石にハマった時つらいか…","ts":"1584724250.068400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"7a7Z"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"b07c465a-4b2e-4363-93df-77e5125101da","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"ここらへん本当覚えることがかなり多いなー\n明日また調べてみます。ありがとうございました","ts":"1584724754.069300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Xa3"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"01770eaa-4c1c-4c65-8a7f-964af6aede12","type":"message","us